Collections.rule:
Individual: @C*
	Types: @B*
	Facts: hasGrammaticalCategory @D*,
		hasLanguage @E*,
		hasNumber @I*,
		hasGender @J*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
		isPreferredLabel @K*(xsd:boolean),
		useIfNegative @L*(xsd:boolean mm:SkipIfEmptyLabel),
		hasLocale @M*
	Annotations: lexicalisation @F*(xsd:string),
		lexicalisation @G*(xsd:string mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
		lexicalisation @H*(xsd:string mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)

Individual: @C*(mm:append(@D*))
	Types: @B*, @A*
	Facts: hasPreposition @E*,
		hasGrammaticalCategory @H*,
		hasLanguage @I*,
		hasSubject @J*,
		hasObject @K* (mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
		isReflexive @L*(xsd:boolean),
		isPassiveForm @M*(xsd:boolean),
		hasLocale @O*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation),
		hasDeterminer @F*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLocation)
	Annotations: lexicalisation @D*(mm:ResolveIfOWLEntityExists)

Class: @B*
	SubClassOf: @A*,
		hasUnit some @F*,
		hasNegativeContribution some @I*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLabel),
		hasSector some @E*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLabel)
	Annotations: definition @D*(xsd:string), 
		rdfs:label @C*(xsd:string),
		hasStandard @G*,
		hasStandard @H*(mm:SkipIfEmptyLabel)
